		<hr size="1">I thought the post on random acts of kindness was great. There have been many nice people on my journeys on Ec'i. Too many to list but thanks to you all.</P><P>I just wanted to start a thread of of people with whom not to do business with.</P><P>I was selling banded armor out front of West Freeport when a fellow I've hunted with a few times named Maxiumus hails me and comments on my new weapon. Me being the proud new owner of a Berserker sword glady offer to let him inspect it. He asks if he may try it out. Having hunted with him a few times in the past I agree(/bonehead). To make a long story short, he ran off with my weapon and laughed at me when i asked for it back.</P><P>The majority of folks I have met have been wonderful. It's just a few players like these that ruin the fun for us all.</P><P>/ignore Maxiumus the Cheat and Thief</P><P><BR><br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
